column5: Thinking of staying at Little Moose Lodge on Clearwater in October. Anyone fished over that way or happened to stay here?
Thinking of staying at Little Moose Lodge on Clearwater in October. Anyone fished over that way or happened to stay here?
The fishing is good and the folks are top shelf. Would recommend it.
The fishing is good and the folks are top shelf. Would recommend it.
Have not fished that chain in a few years.Fished there 8or9 years and thought the fishing was ok. Stayed at little mouse 4or 5 times it is an older lodge but it was adequete.
